<i>adverb</i>: 침착히 [침차키], 초연히 [초연히], 차분히 [차분히], 엄연히 [엄연히], 담담히 [담ː담히], 냉정히 [냉ː정히] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>침착히 [침차키]</dt><br>
<dd>calmly; coolly; composedly</dd><br>
<dd>쉽게 흥분하지 않고 행동이 조심스럽고 차분하게.</dd><br>
<dd>Carefully and calmly in one's action, not being excited easily.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>초연히 [초연히]</dt><br>
<dd>composedly</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 일에 얽매이지 않고 태연하고 의젓하게.</dd><br>
<dd>Without being affected by any incident and in the state of staying calm and mature.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>차분히 [차분히]</dt><br>
<dd>quietly; composedly</dd><br>
<dd>마음이 가라앉아 조용하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of being composed and quiet.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>엄연히 [엄연히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. composedly; refinedly</dd><br>
<dd>사람의 외모나 말, 행동 등이 침착하고 점잖게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a calm and gentle manner in one's appearance, speech, behavior, etc.</dd><br>
<dd>2. undeniably; clearly; definitely</dd><br>
<dd>누구도 부인할 수 없을 정도로 명백하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a manner of being so obvious as to be beyond dispute.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>담담히 [담ː담히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. composedly; calmly</dd><br>
<dd>차분하고 편안하게.</dd><br>
<dd>With a calm and comfortable attitude.</dd><br>
<dd>2. plainly</dd><br>
<dd>글이나 말 내용이 감정적이지 않고 객관적이게.</dd><br>
<dd>Objectively, not expressing oneself emotionally in writing or speaking.</dd><br>
<dd>3. serenely</dd><br>
<dd>물이 맑고 그 움직임이 고요하고 평온하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a state such as that when clean water flows quietly and peacefully.</dd><br>
<dd>4. plainly</dd><br>
<dd>맛이 짜거나 느끼하지 않고 산뜻하고 싱겁게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of tasting fresh and insipid, not salty or greasy.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>냉정히 [냉ː정히]</dt><br>
<dd>calmly; composedly</dd><br>
<dd>생각이나 행동이 감정에 좌우되지 않고 침착하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of one's thinking or behavior being composed and not swayed by one's emotions.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>